room_title: Escape room "1849 Gold Rush" by Paradox Escape Rooms in Valparaiso
room_description:
The year is 1849, and gold has just been discovered in California!
You just received a note from your long lost uncle that says his SECRET GOLD TREASURE MAP WAS STOLEN!
He went to sell his GOLD to the town Assayer, and that was the last time he saw his map. 
He pleads with you to head out west and search through the Assayerâ€™s Office for the map. 
While he distracts the Assayer at the Annual Parade, you will sneak into his office, find the map, and follow it to the Treasure!
Will you strike gold and become an overnight mining magnate or get tossed in the County Jail?
